channel.title: Pwnscape webclient problem
channel.description: hello, im using a server thats compatible with pwnscape v3 client. however i followed a guide to make a web client. Im was having some problems. firstly the ip address the jar is connecting to is always localhost even though in the gui.java its the correct one. secondly alot of buttons were missing in the jar version. Can anyone help me? is there like a guide for this type of server specifically or something? thnks.
